The paper deals with the revision of logic programs, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and logic (cs.LO). The paper also discusses the answer set semantics, which is a topic in programming languages (cs.PL) and databases (cs.DB). Finally, the paper proposes an approach to revising logic programs, which can be seen as a software engineering (cs.SE) problem.
